data.description:
This new construction home’s first floor features 9-foot ceilings, RevWood flooring, open floorplan, kitchen with gas stove/oven, microwave, granite countertops, walk-in pantry all opening to large family room with gas fireplace. Formal dining plus office complete the 1st floor. Upstairs provides 3 secondary bedrooms, a nice loft area and a large Primary suite with vaulted ceiling and over-sized walk-in closet.
GPS Please use 2209 Charlotte Hwy. Sequoia Forest  is a brand new community.
